Enum UnregisteredListenerRef

    • java.lang.Enum<UnregisteredListenerRef>

    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<UnregisteredListenerRef>, ListenerRef

    public enum UnregisteredListenerRef
extends java.lang.Enum<UnregisteredListenerRef>
implements ListenerRef
    A ListenerRef which defines a listener which is already unregistered and will not be notified of events.

    This class is a singleton and its one and only instance can be accessed by INSTANCE.

    Thread safety

    Instances of this class are immutable and as such, safe to be accessed by multiple threads concurrently.

    Synchronization transparency

    The methods of this class are synchronization transparent.
